public void preferResultExternalId(java.lang.String preferredExternalId)
                            throws GnException
Use this option to specify an external identifier which MusicID-File should try to include in any responses that are returned.

Remarks:

This option is currently only supported when online processing is enabled.

Parameters:
preferredExternalId - [in] The name of an external identifier that should be preferred when selecting matches

GnException
